// src/protocol/opcodes.rs

//! MTGO protocol opcode and MagicProperty constants.
//!
//! Opcodes sourced from opcode-table.tsv (generated by tools/opcode-dump).
//! MagicProperty constants sourced from PROTOCOL_RESEARCH.md.

